name: WatchOS UI Kit
description:
Excited to share the start of a WatchOS UI kit!

I've personally always found it hard to get a good UI kit for WatchOS that covers the main items necessary to create a custom app UI. Hopefully you'll find use in this as well!

Built Figma ready with constraints, auto-layout and easy component naming and structuring for easy use. Also includes a lot of text and color styles to easily create any other screens you might need. 

This is a WIP so please send me any suggestions for other screens or components you may need! Fill out this form: https://forms.gle/B8wZV9xManKQ97CF9 or shoot me a message on twitter (@jonrundle)
